{
${WebServer_Text_Area1}.setData("");
var req = new XMLHttpRequest();
//var url = document.location;
//url.href = ${WebServer_Text1}.getData();
req.open('GET', document.location, false);
req.send(null);
var headers = req.getAllResponseHeaders().split("\\r\\n");
${WebServer_Text_Area1}.setData("" + headers.join("\\r\\n"));
if (req.getAllResponseHeaders().indexOf("Content-Encoding: gzip") != -1){
${../Data1}.setValue(" Success: Compression is enabled " + new Date());
}else {
${../Data1}.setValue(" Warning: Compression is not enabled " + new Date());
}
if (req.getAllResponseHeaders().indexOf("Connection: keep-alive") != -1){
${../Data1}.setValue(" Success: Keep-Alive is enabled, make sure Keep-Alive timeout is at least 60 " + new Date());
}else {
${../Data1}.setValue(" Warning: Keep-Alive is not enabled " + new Date());
}

} catch(error){
${WebServer_Text_Area1}.setData(error);
